    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's the way people look at you. i can already see the pity in their eyes. the way they'll talk about me like I was some kid who thought he could play in the big leagues but couldn't hack it. there's no Version 2.0 for this. there's just the crushing reality that i've ruined everything i ever built. it feels like there's no way out of this hole that doesn't involve facing that every single day.",
